{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Prohibit restaurants from including tips on bills",
        "additional_details": "Restaurants are increasingly adding tips as service charges to bills. Although it is still often optional, many customers find it difficult asking for the charge to be removed. We believe this is an American culture that has no place in the UK.",
        "background": "Prohibit restaurants adding tips or \u201cservice charges\u201d to bills, even if they are optional.",
